AI Doesn't Replace Sales

One misconception about AI is that it replaces sales teams.

I see it differently.

Salespeople build relationships.

Managers make decisions.

Revenue leaders create strategy.

AI simply ensures that critical signals don't go unnoticed.

It gives every team better visibility.

The decision still belongs to people.

The Vision

Throughout this handbook we've explored eight different leakage zones.

They may look unrelated.

Lead leakage.

Pipeline leakage.

Forecast leakage.

System leakage.

In reality, they're connected.

The future isn't about solving each problem individually.

It's about building one intelligent system that continuously monitors all of them together.

That's the direction Revenue Operations is moving.

And it's the direction I'm exploring through the workflows and systems I build.

